stream << EOF
ogle_gui is a real DVD player that supports DVD menus and navigation.
It can access CSS-protected DVDs if you have libdvdcss installed, 
take screen shots, and view movies in fullscreen mode.
It handles angles correctly and you can 
switch subtitles and audio tracks.
